{
  "stem": "15732.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we though that in two, three hours we would be in-- in Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were steaming, going and going and going and going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it took a day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And another day we made already a hunger strike.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The captain came on the loudspeaker or whatever he did and told us, it's not going to help you anything if you're on hunger strike.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "English.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "English.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was the English army.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said-- that was an army ship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said to us, I don't know where I go by instructions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I do not know where I am instructed to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I will find out, then I'll let you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the meantime, if you are making a hunger strike, you will be hungry, not I.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was the message.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had one day hunger strike.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The next day, we got-- got some biscuits with the worms were crawling on that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was no yielding from the English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, the English had Aneruin Bevan was-- was the foreign minister, a person that excelled himself and his hatred to anything that was Jewish and anything that had to do with Palestine.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was extremely pro-Arab.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he just thought that he will crush us as he crushed others.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he decided to take us back to France.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After again get eight days that we were on the we arrived in Port-de-Bouc was the name of the place where we arrived.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We arrived om Port-de-Bouc.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there, the captain says, you are ready for the [INAUDIBLE] embarkation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how you say, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Certainly that we did not want to disembark in France.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where are we going to go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Who wants to go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a few-- on the ship, we had a few young men that were French-speaking.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
